<template>
    <swiper
        :slides-per-view="3"
        :space-between="50"
        @swiper="onSwiper"
        @slideChange="onSlideChange"
    >
        <swiper-slid>slide1</swiper-slid>
        <swiper-slid>slide2</swiper-slid>
        <swiper-slid>slide3</swiper-slid>
    </swiper>
</template>

<script>
import {Swiper, SwiperSlide} from 'swiper/vue';
import 'swiper/css';
export default {
    name: 'Swiper',
    components: {
        Swiper,
        SwiperSlide,
    },
    setUp() {
        // return {
        //     onSwiper,
        //     onSlideChange,
        // }
    }
}
</script>
